      "para_id": "Q004965.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Lu-amana , child of Ur-Hendursaĝaka , the brewer , is your servant ."
    }
